{"tid":1565742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚獅子山有[無人機]既都帶埋呀","createTime":"2019-09-13T09:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T14:59:04.000Z","uid":282534,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"53c2949e1a135fca83845f49fc70d4347c1ec64f","tid":1565742,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxgP926.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxgP926.jpg&h=01f88267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnEm09N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnEm09N.jpg&h=29ee1603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好講咁多 上兩張文宣圖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中秋節點可以少一個燈籠架</span></span>，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑暗時代更唔可少一盞明燈</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n913 中秋夜約定大家照亮在地上同在天上嘅同路人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">配合913 獅子山中秋人鏈點燈活動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屆時準備有無人機幻彩飛行活動，<br />\n誠邀各<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Drone</span></span>友參加。<br />\n22世紀科技天燈燈籠點少得你。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燈，全部都係燈</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a632a5f42e802098e9cc9d8d6d0ae69af087d69a","tid":1565742,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:16:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4Qbnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=2351b04c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"7214164468f0d3e0c7ab03e2f4729fc3d7644ca1","tid":1565742,"uid":228092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>915去完英領去民陣遊行！升級玩國際戰線！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋升級玩國際戰線！繼續遍地開花！每個星期去唔同領事館，舉唔同國旗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1559803/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1559803/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBbo7qE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBbo7qE.jpg&h=5a962f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQY3pQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQY3pQn.jpg&h=1db04e57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3d98174e66372a9bb8cb4cacbf99753f0ce57